com.cerner.beadledom.resteasy

Class BuiltGenericResponse<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.ws.rs.core.Response
      • org.jboss.resteasy.specimpl.AbstractBuiltResponse
        • org.jboss.resteasy.specimpl.BuiltResponse
          • com.cerner.beadledom.resteasy.BuiltGenericResponse<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericResponse<T>, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class BuiltGenericResponse<T>
extends org.jboss.resteasy.specimpl.BuiltResponse
implements GenericResponse<T>
    An extension of the resteasy BuiltResponse class with additional implementations for GenericResponse.

    Consumers should avoid depending on this class directly instead preferring to depend on the GenericResponse or Response types. This class is necessary for the internal workings of Resteasy because Resteasy is heavily dependent on the BuiltResponse class.

    Since:
    1.3
    Author:
    John Leacox
    See Also:
    BuiltResponse, GenericResponse
